Title: She Hates Us
Writer: Peter Nowalk (created by), Erika Harrison, Erika Harrison (story editor)
Actors: Viola Davis, Billy Brown, Alfred Enoch, Jack Falahee
Plot: Tensions in the Keating household run high, as each student struggles in their own way trying to return to normalcy. In a flashback, we'll learn new details about Annalise's past.
